<BaseLayout title="Resume" sideBarActiveItemID="cv">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Profile</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-justify space-y-2">
    <p>
      I'm Tien Cheng, a graduate of Singapore Polytechnic (SP) with a Diploma in
      Applied AI and Analytics, and a recipient of the Singapore Computer
      Society Silver Medal. As a former co-founder and operations department
      head of SPAI (an AI Singapore Student Chapter) in AY21/22, I actively
      promoted the field of Data Science during my time at SP.
    </p>
    <p>
      Currently, I'm a full-time national serviceman (i.e conscript) at the <a
        href="https://www.mindef.gov.sg/oms/dis/"
        >Digital and Intelligence Service</a
      >, but I also work on personal projects and competitions in my free time.
      After serving NS, I'll be doing an Computer Science undergrad at the
      National University of Singapore.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Education</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container grid gap-4 mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Diploma in Applied AI and Analytics"
      subtitle="2020 to 2023 at Singapore Polytechnic, Singapore"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-10 grid gap-2">
